---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="TrustMeBro Terms of Service - The rules of the game (we keep it simple)">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen pt-8 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">Terms of</span> Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">the rules we all agree to 📜</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2">Last updated: December 1, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose max-w-none space-y-8">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">TL;DR ⚡</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300">
            <li>• Be cool, don't do illegal stuff</li>
            <li>• Our content is for entertainment/info - verify important facts yourself</li>
            <li>• We can update these terms whenever</li>
            <li>• Using our site = agreeing to these terms</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms 🤝</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            By accessing and using TrustMeBro ("the Site"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. 
            If you don't agree, please don't use the site. Simple as that.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">2. Use of the Site 💻</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes. You agree NOT to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Use the Site in any way that violates laws or regulations</li>
            <li>• Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
            <li>• Interfere with or disrupt the Site or servers</li>
            <li>• Use automated systems (bots, scrapers) without permission</li>
            <li>• Reproduce, duplicate, or copy our content for commercial purposes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">3. Content Disclaimer 📰</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <strong>Important:</strong> TrustMeBro provides news content that has been rewritten and stylized for entertainment purposes. 
            While we source from legitimate news outlets and fact-check where possible:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
            <li>• Content is provided "as is" without warranties</li>
            <li>• We are not responsible for the accuracy of third-party sources</li>
            <li>• For critical decisions, always verify with original sources</li>
            <li>• Our opinions and humor are not professional advice</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">4. Intellectual Property 🎨</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            The Site and its original content, features, and functionality are owned by TrustMeBro and are protected by 
            copyright, trademark, and other intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            You may share our articles on social media with proper attribution. You may not republish our content 
            in full without written permission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">5. Third-Party Services 🔗</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            The Site may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the content, 
            privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We use third-party services including:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 mt-2">
            <li>• Google Analytics (traffic analysis)</li>
            <li>• Google AdSense (advertising)</li>
            <li>• Netlify (hosting)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability ⚖️</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            TrustMeBro shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages 
            resulting from your use of the Site. In no event shall our liability exceed $100 USD.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">7. Changes to Terms 🔄</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will notify users of significant changes by 
            updating the "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold gradient-text mb-4">8. Contact Us 📬</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Questions about these Terms? Hit us up:
          </p>
          <p class="text-cyan-400 mt-2">
            <a href="/contact" class="hover:underline">Contact Form →</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
